title: Kill Tony star Casey Rocket announces debut Australian tour this April
text:
The rising US comic, who earned his spot as a door person at Joe Rogan's Comedy Mothership venue after winning the Austin Comedy Competition, has scheduled appearances across three major cities following his recent sold-out North American tour. Recently named in Deadline's Future of Funny: 15 Comedians Ready to Break Out in 2025 list, Rocket […] Words by Staff Writer
The rising US comic, who earned his spot as a door person at Joe Rogan's Comedy Mothership venue after winning the Austin Comedy Competition, has scheduled appearances across three major cities following his recent sold-out North American tour.
Recently named in Deadline's Future of Funny: 15 Comedians Ready to Break Out in 2025 list, Rocket will perform across seven nights in Melbourne, Sydney and Brisbane.
Casey Rocket Australian tour
Mon 8 Apr – Paddo RSL, Sydney, 8pm
Thu 11 Apr – The Comic's Lounge, Melbourne, 9pm
